      Ali & Matt
    %h2
      Healdsburg CA - 2/22/2014
    %p
      We met while working together at EMI Music in 2009. I (Ali) was working from the Hollywood office while Matt was up in San Francisco. After some changes happened with the team, I was asked to relocate to San Francisco to manage the office and met Matt in person shortly thereafter. If it were up to our co-worker and friend, Evan, we would have started dating long before we actually did … he should really be a professional matchmaker! When Matt finally asked me out, we enjoyed a first date full of sushi and cocktails (not much has changed!) and the conversation flowed freely. A few years, a couple apartments and one noisy cat later, Matt popped the question and here we are planning our dream wedding!
