    %h2
      Ceremony and Reception at Barndiva
    %h3
      231 Center St, Healdsburg CA 95448
    %p
      From the minute I (Ali) walked in, I fell in love! It wasn’t until the next weekend when I brought Matt back (and tasted the food!) that we decided this would be the perfect place to get married. From the beautiful gardens, eclectic art, wonderful wine, refreshing cocktails (and did we mention amazing food?!) Barndiva couldn’t get any better.
    %p
      The ceremony will start promptly at 5pm in the Barndiva restaurant garden. After the ceremony, cocktail hour, dinner & dancing will take place next door at Studio Barndiva, both in the gallery and in the studio garden.
